(40, 11, 8, 23, 20, 2, 2, 'soft raiment', 'Contrast of Clothing and Status', 'This connection highlights the contrast between soft clothing associated with kings and the prophetic act of walking naked and barefoot. Both passages emphasize the rejection of worldly status and the call to humility.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
