(40, 11, 11, 49, 3, 8, 8, 'least in the kingdom of heaven', 'Greatness in the Kingdom', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of being ''least'' in relation to greatness. Matthew highlights that even the least in the kingdom is greater than John, while Ephesians presents the speaker as ''less than the least'' among saints, yet entrusted with a significant mission.', 'theme', 0.363, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
