(40, 11, 11, 42, 9, 48, 48, 'least in the kingdom of heaven', 'Greatness in the Kingdom', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of greatness in the kingdom of heaven, contrasting societal views of greatness with divine standards. Matthew highlights that the least in the kingdom is greater than John the Baptist, while Luke states that the least among you shall be great.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
